ADDITIONAL TERMS

Network Use Provision:
If you run a modified version of this software as a network service,
you must make the complete source code of your modified version
available to users of that service.

Privacy Protection:
Any deployment of this software must maintain the privacy and security
protections defined in the SECURITY.md file, particularly:
- End-to-end encryption for communications
- Anonymous access options for vulnerable users
- Data minimization principles
- GDPR and CCPA compliance

Human Rights Commitment:
This software is designed to support human rights work. Any use of this
software must not violate human rights principles or be used to harm
vulnerable individuals or communities.

